---
// PricingTable.astro — Pricing page, strictly based on HTML reference
---

<!-- Promo Banner -->
<div class="pricing-promo">
  <span class="pricing-promo__icon" aria-hidden="true">🎉</span>
  Join today and get 1 Month of Pro Free
</div>

<!-- ===================== FAQ ===================== -->
<section class="pricing-faq">
  <div class="pricing-faq__inner">
    <h2 class="pricing-faq__title">FAQ</h2>

    <div class="pricing-faq__list">
      <details class="faq-item" open>
        <summary class="faq-item__summary">
          <span>Will Slax Reader really save me hours of reading every week?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-item__body">
          <p>Yes! Our AI summarization and semantic search allow you to extract the most important information from an article in seconds. Instead of reading every word of every bookmark, you can "chat" with your library to find exactly what you need.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-item__summary">
          <span>What does "No auto-renewal" mean?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-item__body">
          <p>We believe in transparency. When your Pro month ends, we won't charge your card automatically. You'll simply be asked if you'd like to continue for another month. No "forgotten subscription" traps here.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-item__summary">
          <span>Can I cancel my subscription?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-item__body">
          <p>Yes, you can cancel at any time from your account settings. You'll continue to have access to your Pro features until the end of your current billing period.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-item__summary">
          <span>Is there a student discount?</span>
          <span class="faq-item__chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-item__body">
          <p>We offer special educational pricing for students and researchers. Please contact our support team with your .edu email address to learn more.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== Bottom CTA ===================== -->
<section class="pricing-cta">
  <div class="pricing-cta__inner">
    <h2 class="pricing-cta__title">Start Your Intelligent Reading Journey Today</h2>
    <p class="pricing-cta__sub">Read smarter, learn faster, remember more.</p>
    <a class="pricing-cta__btn" href="/reader/download">Get Started - It&apos;s Free →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== Styles ===================== -->
<style>
  /* ── Promo Banner ── */
  .pricing-promo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 48px auto 40px;
    max-width: 480px;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #e6fff8;
    border: 1px solid #b2f0df;
    color: #0d7a5f;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .pricing-promo__icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  /* ── Table Wrapper ── */
  .pricing-wrap {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px 80px;
  }

  .pricing-table-scroll {
    overflow-x: auto;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.10);
  }

  /* ── Table ── */
  .pricing-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ── Column widths ── */
  .pricing-table__label-col {
    width: 40%;
    padding: 40px 36px;
    text-align: left;
    vertical-align: middle;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ecf0f5;
  }

  .pricing-table__plan-col {
    width: 30%;
    padding: 40px 28px;
    text-align: center;
    vertical-align: top;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ecf0f5;
  }

  /* Pro column: teal border left+right+top, tinted bg */
  .pricing-table__plan-col--pro {
    border-left: 2px solid #14b8a6;
    border-right: 2px solid #14b8a6;
    border-top: 2px solid #14b8a6;
    background: rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.04);
  }

  /* ── Table title ── */
  .pricing-table__title {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1f1f1f;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  /* ── Plan header inside th ── */
  .pricing-plan {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .pricing-plan__name {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1f1f1f;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .pricing-plan__name--pro {
    color: #14b8a6;
  }

  .pricing-plan__price {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .pricing-plan__amount {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1f1f1f;
  }

  .pricing-plan__period {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #888;
  }

  .pricing-plan__strike {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #aaa;
    text-decoration: line-through;
    margin-left: 4px;
  }

  .pricing-plan__desc {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #888;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 180px;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
  }

  /* ── CTA buttons ── */
  .pricing-plan__btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: #f1f3f5;
    color: #333;
    transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .pricing-plan__btn:hover {
    background: #e2e6ea;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .pricing-plan__btn--pro {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #25d4b0 0%, #14b8a6 100%);
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.25);
  }

  .pricing-plan__btn--pro:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1fc9a7 0%, #0ea596 100%);
    color: #fff;
  }

  /* ── Feature rows ── */
  .pricing-table__feature {
    padding: 20px 36px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ecf0f5;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #333;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: left;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .pricing-table__cell {
    padding: 20px 28px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ecf0f5;
    text-align: center;
    vertical-align: middle;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .pricing-table__cell--pro {
    border-left: 2px solid #14b8a6;
    border-right: 2px solid #14b8a6;
    background: rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.04);
  }

  /* last row: no bottom border */
  .pricing-table__last-row .pricing-table__feature,
  .pricing-table__last-row .pricing-table__cell {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .pricing-table__cell--pro-last {
    border-bottom: 2px solid #14b8a6;
    border-radius: 0 0 18px 0;
  }

  /* ── Check / Cross icons ── */
  .check {
    color: #14b8a6;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .cross {
    color: #ccc;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  /* ── AI badge ── */
  .ai-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-right: 6px;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: #e6fff8;
    color: #0d7a5f;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  /* ── FAQ ── */
  .pricing-faq {
    padding: 64px 0 80px;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }

  .pricing-faq__inner {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .pricing-faq__title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1f1f1f;
    margin: 0 0 40px;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .pricing-faq__list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .faq-item__summary {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #1f1f1f;
    transition: background 0.2s ease;
  }

  .faq-item__summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item[open] .faq-item__summary {
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .faq-item__summary:hover {
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .faq-item__chevron {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #aaa;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease;
  }

  .faq-item[open] .faq-item__chevron {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .faq-item__body {
    padding: 4px 24px 20px;
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .faq-item__body p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* ── Bottom CTA ── */
  .pricing-cta {
    padding: 72px 0 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #2eb396 0%, #5edda8 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pricing-cta__inner {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .pricing-cta__title {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .pricing-cta__sub {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #ffffff;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin: 0 0 40px;
  }

  .pricing-cta__btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 14px 36px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #1f1f1f;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .pricing-cta__btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
  }
</style>

<!-- ===================== Pricing Table ===================== -->
<div class="pricing-wrap">
  <div class="pricing-table-scroll">
    <table class="pricing-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <!-- Col 1: label -->
          <th class="pricing-table__label-col">
            <h2 class="pricing-table__title">Pricing Plans</h2>
          </th>

          <!-- Col 2: Free -->
          <th class="pricing-table__plan-col">
            <div class="pricing-plan">
              <h3 class="pricing-plan__name">Free</h3>
              <div class="pricing-plan__price">
                <span class="pricing-plan__amount">$0</span>
                <span class="pricing-plan__period">/ Month</span>
              </div>
              <p class="pricing-plan__desc">
                Unlimited bookmarks &amp; backup forever — join now before limits apply!
              </p>
              <a class="pricing-plan__btn" href="/reader/download">Start Free</a>
            </div>
          </th>

          <!-- Col 3: Pro Reader -->
          <th class="pricing-table__plan-col pricing-table__plan-col--pro">
            <div class="pricing-plan">
              <h3 class="pricing-plan__name pricing-plan__name--pro">Pro Reader</h3>
              <div class="pricing-plan__price">
                <span class="pricing-plan__amount">$5.99</span>
                <span class="pricing-plan__period">/ Month</span>
                <span class="pricing-plan__strike">($9.99)</span>
              </div>
              <p class="pricing-plan__desc">
                Unleash your reading superpowers with integrated AI analysis.
              </p>
              <a class="pricing-plan__btn pricing-plan__btn--pro" href="/reader/download">
                Try 1 Month Free
              </a>
            </div>
          </th>
        </tr>
      </thead>

      <tbody>
        <!-- Row 1 -->
        <tr>
          <td class="pricing-table__feature">Save unlimited articles, websites, posts.</td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell pricing-table__cell--pro"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Row 2 -->
        <tr>
          <td class="pricing-table__feature">Permanent snapshots. Anti-404 backup for every articles.</td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell pricing-table__cell--pro"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Row 3 -->
        <tr>
          <td class="pricing-table__feature">Unlimited highlights and notes.</td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell pricing-table__cell--pro"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Row 4 -->
        <tr>
          <td class="pricing-table__feature">Full-text search for all articles in your Slax Reader collection.</td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell pricing-table__cell--pro"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Row 5 -->
        <tr>
          <td class="pricing-table__feature">Sync your articles across web, iOS, and Android</td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell pricing-table__cell--pro"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Row 6 -->
        <tr>
          <td class="pricing-table__feature">Share articles highlights and join discussions with friends.</td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell pricing-table__cell--pro"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Row 7 -->
        <tr>
          <td class="pricing-table__feature">Open source on GitHub. Fully transparent. You own your data.</td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell pricing-table__cell--pro"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Row 8 -->
        <tr>
          <td class="pricing-table__feature">Create tags to easily organize your articles manually</td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell pricing-table__cell--pro"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Row 9 — AI -->
        <tr>
          <td class="pricing-table__feature">
            <span class="ai-badge">✨AI</span>
            Smart auto-tagging for effortless organization. AI categorizes for you.
          </td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell"><span class="cross" aria-label="Not included">✗</span></td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell pricing-table__cell--pro"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Row 10 — AI -->
        <tr>
          <td class="pricing-table__feature">
            <span class="ai-badge">✨AI</span>
            Instant Summaries: Get the gist in 3 seconds.
          </td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell"><span class="cross" aria-label="Not included">✗</span></td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell pricing-table__cell--pro"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Row 11 — AI -->
        <tr>
          <td class="pricing-table__feature">
            <span class="ai-badge">✨AI</span>
            Interactive Outlines: Grasp any 10,000-word essay in 30 seconds.
          </td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell"><span class="cross" aria-label="Not included">✗</span></td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell pricing-table__cell--pro"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Row 12 — AI (last row, no bottom border) -->
        <tr class="pricing-table__last-row">
          <td class="pricing-table__feature">
            <span class="ai-badge">✨AI</span>
            Chatbot: Deep dive into any topic by directly chatting with your articles.
          </td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell"><span class="cross" aria-label="Not included">✗</span></td>
          <td class="pricing-table__cell pricing-table__cell--pro pricing-table__cell--pro-last"><span class="check" aria-label="Included">✓</span></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>
